summary: An ordinance relating to and amending Plat 57E, page 143 of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in Lots 4-6 incl., Block 76, Lots 1-6, incl., Block 77, all in Moss' 2nd Add. to Seattle, Lots 14-19 incl., Block 5, Jefferson Park Add., located on both sides of Columbian Way in vicinity of Spokane St. from Duplex Residence High Density (RD 5000) Zone to Multiple Residence Low Density (RM) Zone.
